gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 126, Raptors 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Raptors, 126-107.  Paolo Banchero led the way with 25 points, five rebounds and three assists, while Jalen Suggs added 18 points, four assists and two steals in the victory.  Dennis Schroder tallied 24 points and four 3pt. FG for the Raptors in the losing effort.  The Magic improve to 9-5 on the season, 2-1 in IST, while the Raptors fall to 6-8 and 0-2 in IST play.
